          "en": "The Messenger of Allah (peace be upon him and his family) said: Blessed is he who lives a long life and beautifies his actions, for his ending will be good since his Lord, Mighty and Majestic, is pleased with him. And woe to he who lives a long life and commits evil, for his ending will be evil since his Lord, Mighty and Majestic, is discontented with him.",
